  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Asharak is triumphant and emotional after his people stood against impossible odds.",
    "how_to_trigger": "Repro steps:1. Start the game2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A3. oe readyattackonden4. goto 195.23, 34.85, 441.72 and skip through the entreance cinematic.5. Kill Zevlor (CTRL-K)6. Blow the horn and side with the tieflings.7. Killcombat8. Wait for the cinematic to start."
