                                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                                      "children": {
                                                        "14": {
                                                          "id": "14",
                                                          "speaker": "Asharak",
                                                          "text": "Wouldn't like to be in Kagha's shoes about now - but he'll have kinder words for you, I wager.",
                                                          "context": "NodeContext: Gently urging you on - someone has to be catch Halsin up on what happened, and he's probably not going to like it",
                                                          "checkflags": [
